# INSTALL PLUGIN
#
#        three defined variables are mandatory which contain snippets of bash code:
#        - prescript
#        - partscript
#        - postscript
#
#        these snippets will be in addition to what's defined for the node or group configuration

# Plugin selection based on the following search path and priority:
#
# 1 node name                 e.g. plugins/install/node001.py
# 2 group name                e.g. plugins/install/compute.py
# 3 default                   e.g. plugins/install/default.py
